    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>
        Redesigned an adiabatic Flash comparator and 3-bit priority encoder using
        SCRL-based adiabatic logic gates, reducing power by an estimated 7.2x versus a
        double-tailed comparator and 19x–33x versus standard CMOS.
      </li>
      <li>
        Ran post-extraction simulations to analyze parasitic capacitance and refine
        transistor-level sizing for power optimization.
      </li>
    </ul>

